title: Who's the best marching band in the Lansing region?
text:
Welcome to the Greater Lansing High School Sports Best Band Contest! 
The Lansing State Journal is looking for the best high school marching band in the Greater Lansing region. 
We want the bands with the best rah-rah tunes who always get the home crowd fired up, who own the field during halftime, and who let their amazing sound do their talking for them. Only one local band can claim the title as the #1 High School Band in the Greater Lansing region. Is your band worthy? 
If your high school band rocks on and off the field, enter them in the contest then gather your friends and family to vote! The 3 bands with most votes will be considered our finalists and be invited to our Greater Lansing High School Sports Awards Banquet, where the winner will be announced and presented with an award. Plus you'll get bragging rights! Good luck.
